div1.p: United States Circuit Court, District of Washington
In re M. L. Coovert vs. Habeas Corpus
Filed June 12 1893 A Reeves Ayres Clerk. R.M. Hopkins Deputy Clerk.
C. E. S. Wood For petitioner
Lowman & Hanford S.&P. Co's Blank No. 90. Praecipe - U. S. Court.
In red M. L. Coovert vs. Habeas Corpus
Notice:-- Arrotneys will please endorse their own filings. Rule 47.
To the Clerk of the above entitled Court: you will please enter my appearance as solicitor for petitioner in the above entitled cause.
CES Wood Solicitor of Williams & Wood attys.
Notice:-- Attorneys will please endorse their own filings. Rule 47.
